        "13.7%"
      ],
      "summary": "26/2017 When we look at major division of food and non -food commodities, which holds large share in the commodity basket, the magnitude of Food and Non -alcoholic beverages inflation rate at August EFY2017 showed 12.7% as compared to the same month in the previous year. From Food and Non -Alcoholic Beverage aspect, the highest weight is hoed by Bread and Cereals, Vegetables, Other -Food products, Non -Alcoholic Beverage, and Meat; whose inflation at August EFY2017 is recorded  a decrease for Bread & Cereals ( -1.9%); Vegetables increased by (19.3%); Other -Food products (Food products not  elsewhere  classified)  increased  by (22.8%); Meat  increased  by (12.1%) and Non -Alcoholic  Beverages &  coffee  increased by (56.0%) .",
